description: This charming condo offers a cozy and comfortable living space in a convenient location. Perfect for a small family, couples, or individuals looking for a stylish and affordable home. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting living area that boasts ample natural light and an open floor plan. The kitchen features an exposed brick modern kitchen, sleek countertops, and plenty of cabinet space for all your culinary needs. The bedrooms are well-sized and provide a peaceful retreat after a long day. Enjoy the convenience of low-maintenance living with its manageable size and efficient layout. Many nearby shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and entertainment options. The building also provides shared amenities such as a common roof deck where you can relax and enjoy beautiful views of the surrounding area. Commuting is a breeze with public transportation just steps from your door.  Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a lovely condo in a sought-after location
